This is the tooltip button. Clicking on this button opens the tooltip menu , from where you can control
The Distraction Shield. We'll have a look at it now. Click 'Next' to continue.
Clicking this button will add the current website to your personal blacklist .
Now, when you will enter this website you will be redirected. This helps you add all your
sites to a blacklist fast and easy. Click 'Next' to continue.
Wanna know how much time you save? Click here and find interesting statistics.

Do you want to customize your experience?
By pressing this button you can open the options page.
Here you can select which mode you want The Distraction Shield to use.
Do you feel Lazy? With this mode you will always have the option of skipping your exercise.
With Pro, you will make the most of your time, cause every time you enter one of your blocked
sites, you will have to solve a set of exercises .
Use the slider to chose how often you want to be redirected.
<i> For example if you chose 10 minutes,
after being redirected once, you will not be redirected again for another 10 minutes.

Here you can see the list of websites that you will be redirected from.
You
can deselect a site to disable redirection on that site temporarily, or remove it
You can add a site to the blacklist here. Just enter the address and hit save.
You can use this slider to disable The Distraction Shield temporarily. Select the
amount of time you want and click ’Turn Off’.
Thanks for choosing The Distraction Shield and Happy Learning!
